#

Grilled Herb-Crusted Sirloin Steak

$25.99
700 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BeefGrilledMain Course

Description

Juicy sirloin steak infused with fresh herbs, grilled to perfection.

Ingredients

  • Sirloin steak: 1 lb
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
